            <ul>Types of RTOS:
                <li>Hard Real-Time</li> 
                <li>Firm Real-Time</li>
                <li>Soft Real-Time</li>
              </ul>
              RTOS is used in Air traffic control systems, Anti-lock Brake Systems, and Heart pacemakers
         </fieldset>
