                <li>It manages RAM memory so that all running processes and programs can work effectively and efficiently.</li>
                <li>It also controls and manages all primary tasks of the OS as well as manages access and use of various peripherals connected to the computer.</li>
                <li>It schedules the work done by the CPU so that the work of each user is executed as efficiently as possible.</li>
