            <u>Example:</u> QNX, Mac OS X, K42, etc.<br>
            
            <b>Monolithic Kernel:</b> It is an OS architecture that supports all basic features of computer components such as resource management, memory, file, etc. <br>
            <u>Example:</u> Solaris, DOS, OpenVMS, Linux, etc.
